3. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with video data and its analysis, which falls under the domain of multimedia. 
4. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper deals with the analysis of moving vehicles, which can be seen as a network of objects. 
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses sparse reconstruction algorithms, which are commonly used in machine learning.
